Web Crawler
	List all used elements, classes, and ID's
	Find used CSS files, download their contents
	Follow pages with same domain, crawl each one for used elements/css

CSS Optimizer
	Preserve/Remove Comments
	Sort Selectors
	Sort Properties
	Optimize Shorthands
	Regroup Selectors
	Fix cases
	Remove redundant/duplicate rules

CSS Minifier
	Remove whitespace
	Combine like selectors

UI
	Ability to enter URL to be crawled
	Ability to upload CSS file(s)
	Ability to paste CSS
